{"tid":2145252,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD教主(ptt網名：obov)於AMD 2蚊時all in全副身家120萬美金買AMD","createTime":"2020-08-08T03:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T03:37:14.000Z","uid":351468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"60b9e1ae39c10b2b1342109a1ee80fd18e37e207","tid":2145252,"uid":351468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"目前身家約5000萬美金"},{"pid":"06fc55b7a49178b6fe33e050500d7b58af70143e","tid":2145252,"uid":29381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:15:51.000Z","msg":"obov是 ptt 的名人，以發文推文的個人特色而出名。常因爭議性的發言用語而被水桶，也稱作水桶哥[1]，後來又被稱作母豬教主（參見母豬教）簡稱教主。<br />\n<br />\n自稱自己為「美國阿爸人」，以高高在上的態度貶低母國台灣為東南亞糞島，貶低台灣民族自尊<br />\n<br />\n又因為仇女言論被八卦版水桶，於股版宣稱台灣6~7年級的世代無法和中國龐大的人才競爭#1UYY8BMb (stock)<br />\n<br />\n年過35，仍是一個孤單未婚之人，於stock板#1TltwNZ1 (Stock)下推文，澄清關於有傳聞說自己娶日本老婆一事是假的<br />\n<br />\n想問有乜好吹奏?"},{"pid":"86e5d925c319e80ded39b10fa07853a21d0ff889","tid":2145252,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:23:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f043b0bd153954e7f0e614704b5bcec8b7ef0ba","tid":2145252,"uid":64073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"now all in INTC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d07145b07d90c4677a1730ebc3fddf7bcd2903","tid":2145252,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:37:14.000Z","msg":"全副身家120萬美"}]}